These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
City: marseilles, colone
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| City     | marseilles     | colone      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
There 2 different types of food: garlic, pepper
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Food     | pepper   | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre         | salsa   | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Sport          | weightlifting | ice-hockey |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, september
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Birthday        | june      | september  |
| Sport       | rugby     | cricket    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

