.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, scientist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, r&b
1. the scientist is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Flower         | rose | marigold    |
| Job           | bartender   | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | classical |

