.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, coach
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, superhero
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, lavender
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who likes green##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Job           | coach     | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy  |
| Color     | lavender      | green |

