2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, van
1. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | thai     | german   |
| Pet         | goat | frog |
| Transport     | car      | van      |

